data.description: Nestled within a serene neighborhood, this delightful property unveils a cozy living room that beckons with warmth and comfort. This residence features two equally inviting bedrooms, offering ample space for relaxation and rest. Step onto refinished hardwood floors that add a touch of elegance and durability to the interior ambiance. Beyond the confines of the home, discover a spacious fenced level backyard, providing a perfect retreat for outdoor activities and gatherings. Imaginations soar with the opportunity to expand and enhance this already impressive property, thanks to its generously sized lot. Professionally landscaped surroundings elevate the appeal of the exterior, creating an inviting environment for both residents and guests alike. Don't miss the chance to make this your own haven, where cozy interiors and expansive outdoor space harmonize to offer the ultimate in comfortable living!
